多家航司表示暂未收到复航通知，但东航武汉公司已在开展试飞等准备工作文/《财经》记者 陈亮 王静仪 编辑/施智梁3月8日，湖北机场集团有限公司下发通知，要求集团职能部门和各版块公司职能部门3月10日开始正常到岗上班。
Several airlines said they had not received the notice, but China Eastern Wuhan Company is already carrying out test flights and other preparatory work. Chen Liang Wang Jing-yi, editor / Shi Zhiliang March 8, Hubei Airport Group Co., Ltd. issued a notice requiring functional departments of the Group and the functional departments of the various sections of the company to start regular work on March 10.
湖北机场集团还要求各支线机场在3月12日前完成复工复航准备工作，各版块公司在3月16日前完成复工复航准备工作。
Hubei Airport Group also required all feeder airports by March 12 to complete preparations for resumption of work, each block of the company by March 16 to complete preparations for resumption of work.
2020.1.10-1.23天河机场每日航班量。
2020.1.10-1.23 Number of daily flights at River Airport.
数据来源：飞友科技2019年40天春运期间天河机场每日航班量。
Source: Feifei Technology 2019 40-day Spring Games Tianhe Airport during the daily flight volume.
数据来源：飞友科技随着湖北疫情得到控制，湖北省内最重要的机场——天河机场真的要复航了吗？武汉天河机场宣传处工作人员向《财经》记者表示，目前只是召回部分管理人员，为复工复航做好准备。
With the outbreak of the disease under control in Hubei Province, will the Tianhe airport, the most important airport in Hubei Province, really resume flights? Staff at Wuhan Tianhe Airport publicity office told Caijing that some managers were recalled just to prepare for the resumption of work.
具体复航时间仍需等待进一步通知。
The exact time of return is subject to further notification.
武汉天河机场也做好相关复航预案。
Wuhan Tianhe Airport also made the relevant plans for the resumption of flights.
多家航司的工作人员对《财经》记者表示，尚没有收到何时复航的通知。
Several crew members told Caijing that they had not yet been notified when the flights would resume.
吉祥航空（603885.SH）方面称，吉祥航空将在做好严防乘机过程交叉感染的情况下，配合民航局和机场做好复航相关工作。
China Airways (603885. SH) said that auspicious airlines will cooperate with the Civil Aviation Administration and airports in the event of cross-infection.
武汉天河机场是国内大型机场，日常业务繁忙。
Wuhan Tianhe Airport is a large domestic airport, daily business is busy.
从暂停商业客运到恢复常态化航班运行，各项准备工作十分繁重。
Preparations range from the suspension of commercial passenger traffic to the resumption of normal flights.
天河机场根据工作需求，提前为复航做好人员培训、设备检修、安全检查等工作，属于必要的安排。
Tianhe Airport according to the work requirements, in advance for the resumption of the training of personnel, equipment overhaul, security inspection and other work, is a necessary arrangement.
中国东方航空武汉有限责任公司（下称“东航武汉公司”）也在为复工复航做相应准备。
China Eastern Airlines Wuhan Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as "Donghang Wuhan Company") is also preparing for the resumption of work.
东航武汉公司党工部工作人员告诉《财经》记者，已于两周前开始做复工复航准备工作。
China Eastern Wuhan Company staff told Caijing that two weeks ago, the resumption of work began to prepare for the resumption of work.
员工一直处于待命状态。
Employees are always on standby.
东航武汉公司的飞行员正在进行适航训练。
The pilot of Dong Hang Wuhan Company is having airworthiness training.
《财经》记者了解到，东航武汉公司飞行部选派8名骨干飞行员分两组参与初始运行。
"Caijing" reporter learned that the Wuhan Company of China Eastern Airlines selected eight backbone pilots in two groups to participate in the initial operation.
技术公司武汉分公司、实业公司在3月2日凌晨4点，将2架飞机恢复到适航状态；综合管理部及时为机组成员配发防护用品，并做好航前体检。
The Wuhan branch of the technology company and the industrial company restored the two aircraft to airworthiness at 4 a.m. on March 2. The Ministry of Integrated Management promptly distributed protective equipment to the crew members and made pre-flight medical checks.
3月2日，由东航武汉公司副总经理丁志荣带队执行民航湖北地区疫情期间第一飞，在不载客的状态下，实现首次飞机持续适航初始本场运行。
On March 2, 2006, Ding Zhirong, deputy general manager of Wuhan Company of China Eastern Airlines, flew the first flight during the period of the civil aviation epidemic in Hubei Province.
3月7日，东航武汉公司再次组织三个不载客本场训练计划，这也是自公司停产以来第二次训练。
On March 7, Wuhan Eastern Airlines again organized three no-passenger training program, this is also the company's second training since the shutdown.
天河机场和湖北省内支线机场何时复航，还要由国家统一部署和省市新冠肺炎疫情防控指挥部来做决定。
The decision on when to resume flights at Tianhe Airport and the Hubei Provincial Spur Line Airport will have to be made by the unified state deployment and the provincial and municipal command for the prevention and control of Newly Coronet Pneumonia.
在关闭离汉离鄂通道后，武汉机场暂停了商业客运，但为保障全省疫情防控，机场仍保持了正常工作状态，例如接各地医疗队的航班以及防疫物资的货运航班。
Wuhan airport has suspended commercial passenger transport after the closure of the Han-Hubei corridor, but has maintained normal operations, such as receiving flights of medical teams and cargo flights for epidemic prevention and control throughout the province.
上述航班量对于武汉天河这样的大型机场商业运营来说杯水车薪。
The above-mentioned flights for Wuhan Tianhe such a large airport commercial operations are small.
1月23日前后本是传统的40天春运旺季，天河机场却在2020年损失了不少客源。
Around January 23, the traditional 40-day Spring Festival, Tianhe Airport lost many customers in 2020.
飞友科技数据显示，今年春运第一天（1月10日）至武汉封城之日，武汉天河机场计划执行4325班客运航班，实际执行3877班。
Wuhan Tianhe Airport plans to carry out 4,325 passenger flights between the first day of the Spring Festival (January 10) and the end of Wuhan on January 10, according to Feipu data.
实际执行量相较于去年同期，下降了53.6%。
Actual delivery decreased by 53.6 per cent compared with the same period last year.
在2020之前，每年春运期间，武汉天河机场旅客吞吐量都能实现快速增长。
Until 2020, Wuhan Tianhe airport passenger throughput can achieve rapid growth during the annual Spring Festival.
2019年1月21日-23日分别运送旅客7.06万人次、7.23万人次、7.46万人次，同比分别增长16.06%、22.69%、20.18%。
From 21 to 23 January 2019, 70,600, 72,300 and 74,600 respectively, representing increases of 16.06 per cent, 22.69 per cent and 20.18 per cent respectively.
天河机场此前预计今年起降航班架次总量2.46万架次，日均起降航班595架次；旅客吞吐总量将达352万人次，日均客流量达8.2万人次，同比增长8%。
The airport had expected 24,600 flights this year, with an average of 595 daily flights. The total number of passengers handled will reach 3.52 million, with an average daily passenger flow of 82,000, an increase of 8 per cent.
预计中的2020年“春运”高峰期正是节前的1月21-23日和节后的1月29-30日，预计日均航班量达600余架次，日均客流达9万人次。
The forecast 2020 "Spring Festival" peak period is January 21-23 before the festival and January 29-30 after the festival, with an expected daily average of more than 600 flights, with an average daily passenger flow of 90,000.
在疫情之下，这些预期最后都落空。
In the face of the epidemic, those expectations were ultimately disappointed.
